#include<stdio.h>

int leap(int n)
{
		if(n%4==0)
		{
			if(n%100==0)
			{
				if(n%400==0)				
					return 1;	
				else
					return 0;
			}
			else
				return 1;
		}
		else
			return 0;
}


int main()
{
    char date[11];
    int n,olu,year,dt,leap_yr,mon,j,h=0,t=0,o=0;
    //printf("Enter the number of test cases:");
    char ch='0';
    scanf("%d",&n);

    for(olu=n;olu>0;olu--)
    {
        //printf("Enter the date:");
        scanf("%s",date);
        dt=((int)date[0]-(int)ch)*10+((int)date[1]-(int)ch);
        year=((int)date[10]-(int)ch)+((int)date[9]-(int)ch)*10+((int)date[8]-(int)ch)*100+((int)date[7]-(int)ch)*1000;
        leap_yr=leap(year);
        //printf("olu%d",olu);
        if(date[3]=='J'&&date[4]=='A'&&date[5]=='N')
            mon=1;
        else if(date[3]=='F'&&date[4]=='E'&&date[5]=='B')
            mon=2;
        else if(date[3]=='M'&&date[4]=='A'&&date[5]=='R')
            mon=3;
        else if(date[3]=='A'&&date[4]=='P'&&date[5]=='R')
            mon=4;
        else if(date[3]=='M'&&date[4]=='A'&&date[5]=='Y')
            mon=5;
        else if(date[3]=='J'&&date[4]=='U'&&date[5]=='N')
            mon=6;
        else if(date[3]=='J'&&date[4]=='U'&&date[5]=='L')
            mon=7;
        else if(date[3]=='A'&&date[4]=='U'&&date[5]=='G')
            mon=8;
        else if(date[3]=='S'&&date[4]=='E'&&date[5]=='P')
            mon=9;
        else if(date[3]=='O'&&date[4]=='C'&&date[5]=='T')
            mon=10;
        else if(date[3]=='N'&&date[4]=='O'&&date[5]=='V')
            mon=11;
        else if(date[3]=='D'&&date[4]=='E'&&date[5]=='C')
            mon=12;
        else
            mon=-1;
            //printf("Date %d Month %d Year %d olu%d\n",dt,mon,year,olu);
        for(j=1;j<mon;j++)
        {
            if(j%2==0)
            {
                if(j==2)
                {
                    if(leap_yr==1)
                        h+=29;
                    else
                        h+=28;
                }
                else if(j>=8)
                    h+=31;
                else
                    h+=30;
            }
            else
            {
                if(j>=9)
                    h+=30;
                else
                    h+=31;
            }
        }
        h+=dt;
        if(h>300)
        {
            t=h-300;
            h=300;
            if(t>60)
            {
                o=t-60;
                t=60;
            }
        }
        //printf("Hundreds: %d \n Tens: %d \n Ones: %d",h,t,o);
        printf("Case %d: ",n-olu+1);
        if(o!=0)
            printf("%d Ones",o);
        else if(t!=0)
            printf("%d Tens",t);
        else
            printf("%d Hundreds",h);
        printf("\n");
        h=0;
        t=0;
        o=0;
    }
    return 0;
}
